import React,{useState,useEffect}from'react';import axios from'axios';export default function useCategory(){const[categories,setCategories]=useState([]);//get category
const getCategories=async()=>{try{const{data}=await axios.get('http://localhost:8080/api/v1/category/get-category');setCategories(data===null||data===void 0?void 0:data.category);}catch(error){console.log(error);}};useEffect(()=>{getCategories();},[]);return categories;}
